{"prompt": "Develop an engaging platform for a virtual event management company. The primary color should be a lively magenta.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Virtual Event Masters</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e6007e; /* Lively Magenta */\n            --secondary-color: #f0b3d1; /* Lighter shade of magenta */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .features-grid, .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item, .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover, .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3, .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .features-grid, .services-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Virtual Event Masters</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Unforgettable Online Experiences</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We specialize in designing and executing seamless virtual events, from intimate webinars to large-scale international conferences. Our mission is to connect your audience and achieve your goals, no matter the distance.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Event Strategy & Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive planning from conception to execution, ensuring all your objectives are met.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Platform Design & Customization</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored virtual environments that reflect your brand and enhance user experience.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Engagement & Interactivity</h3>\n                    <p>Tools and strategies to keep your attendees actively involved and connected.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Technical Support & Production</h3>\n                    <p>Reliable, high-quality streaming and on-demand technical assistance.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"features\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Innovation</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging the latest technology for cutting-edge virtual events.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Expertise</h3>\n                    <p>A dedicated team of event professionals with virtual domain knowledge.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Scalability</h3>\n                    <p>Solutions that adapt to events of any size and complexity.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Impact</h3>\n                    <p>Maximizing reach and engagement to deliver measurable results.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Ready to Host Your Next Virtual Event?</h2>\n            <p>Let's discuss how we can bring your vision to life. Get in touch today!</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"location.href='mailto:info@virtualeventmasters.com'\">Get a Quote</button>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Virtual Event Masters. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a> |\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a> |\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}